commit message: Fix name suggestion usage in tag form editor.

Added support for directly using the name suggestion index from the
'New' action mode, currently only enable when the form UI is enabled.
Bumped android version and build number.

Fix problem with some preset results not being included in final result
set.
Clean fix for TreeSet issue without breaking compareTo contract.

Make selecting a location/bounding box in the box picker work

Make selecting a location/bounding box in the box picker and then not
loading it actually work. Some more protection against potential race
conditions in onResume.
Add labeling of tagged nodes if no icon is found/shown

Enable tag pasting in form UI, correctly finish actionmode when deleting
in PropertyEditor, correctness fixes.
Delete, Copy and Cut of tags in form UI.

Explicitly hide nav bar in onResume and don't rely on
onWindowFocusChanged
Further work on trying to make nav bar hiding reliable.
Fix regression when displaying multiple values.
Properly escape delimiter character in multi-selects.
Updated preset and translations, bumped build number.
Sort combo and multi-select values coreectly.
Better support for localized/internationalized name tags.
Protect against really broken NMEA sentences (from Samsung)

Force dropdown and softkeyboard to appear immediately in the name
selection dialog.
Added further links within help pages.

Merge pull request #447 from bjohas/master

Update of documentation/docs/help/en
